1
00:00:21,840 --> 00:00:23,260
♪Wandering alone♪

2
00:00:23,260 --> 00:00:25,540
♪Walking far by dusk-lit streets♪

3
00:00:25,540 --> 00:00:27,430
♪Your eyes are as cold as clouds♪

4
00:00:27,430 --> 00:00:28,970
♪Faintly coming into view♪

5
00:00:28,970 --> 00:00:30,360
♪The city lights♪

6
00:00:30,360 --> 00:00:32,630
♪Lit up that single moment♪

7
00:00:32,630 --> 00:00:36,140
♪I can't hide or stop missing you♪

8
00:00:36,140 --> 00:00:37,640
♪I can't forget those moments♪

9
00:00:37,640 --> 00:00:39,280
♪Losing you♪

10
00:00:39,610 --> 00:00:41,320
♪Like the seasons in my memory♪

11
00:00:41,320 --> 00:00:43,290
♪Without winter♪

12
00:00:43,290 --> 00:00:44,920
♪Walking down the long, dark street♪

13
00:00:44,920 --> 00:00:46,460
♪Snow will never fall again♪

14
00:00:46,460 --> 00:00:48,200
♪Our old story was torn♪

15
00:00:48,200 --> 00:00:50,610
♪Into scattered pieces♪

16
00:00:50,610 --> 00:00:53,430
♪Replaying every single scene♪

17
00:00:53,430 --> 00:00:55,980
♪After you left♪

18
00:00:57,530 --> 00:01:00,510
♪As if our documentary♪

19
00:01:00,510 --> 00:01:03,120
♪Lost winter♪

20
00:01:04,770 --> 00:01:07,180
♪The breeze speaks of good times♪

21
00:01:07,180 --> 00:01:11,080
♪Pure white devotion♪

22
00:01:11,680 --> 00:01:13,990
♪Send out a letter♪

23
00:01:14,300 --> 00:01:17,780
♪Carrying my longing♪

24
00:01:17,780 --> 00:01:20,980
=The Double Game=

25
00:01:21,020 --> 00:01:23,940
=Episode 14=

26
00:01:36,640 --> 00:01:37,480
Tingxiao.

27
00:01:38,790 --> 00:01:39,760
Explain yourself.

28
00:01:41,350 --> 00:01:43,120
What's going on with Zhi'er?

29
00:01:44,790 --> 00:01:45,630
Dad,

30
00:01:46,680 --> 00:01:48,070
Zhi'er just became the CEO.

31
00:01:48,519 --> 00:01:49,599
She's under huge pressure.

32
00:01:49,820 --> 00:01:51,400
As her brother-in-law, I comforted her.

33
00:01:51,920 --> 00:01:52,846
What's wrong with that?

34
00:01:54,230 --> 00:01:56,430
Did you have to hold her that tight?

35
00:01:59,040 --> 00:02:00,280
Your little scheme

36
00:02:01,040 --> 00:02:01,950
won't get past me.

37
00:02:03,710 --> 00:02:05,760
Dad, since you've made up your mind,

38
00:02:06,230 --> 00:02:07,310
why ask me at all?

39
00:02:10,960 --> 00:02:13,080
You young people's love drama

40
00:02:13,560 --> 00:02:14,470
is no big deal.

41
00:02:15,000 --> 00:02:16,280
That means nothing to me.

42
00:02:17,150 --> 00:02:18,590
As long as you know your limits

43
00:02:19,240 --> 00:02:20,870
and don't make it public

44
00:02:21,310 --> 00:02:22,960
or bring shame to the Lu family,

45
00:02:23,800 --> 00:02:24,910
whatever you do,

46
00:02:25,910 --> 00:02:27,960
I'll let it slide.

47
00:02:29,190 --> 00:02:30,080
But lately,

48
00:02:31,840 --> 00:02:34,030
I've been hearing rumors.

49
00:02:35,560 --> 00:02:37,630
That's not just fooling around.

50
00:02:39,750 --> 00:02:40,710
Someone told me

51
00:02:41,280 --> 00:02:43,280
you reported the illegal reclamation

52
00:02:44,280 --> 00:02:45,590
of Lianxin Island

53
00:02:46,430 --> 00:02:48,030
and arranged

54
00:02:48,310 --> 00:02:49,400
the later unauthorized work.

55
00:02:51,560 --> 00:02:52,870
Do you have anything to say?

56
00:02:57,080 --> 00:02:58,800
Dad, how can you believe that?

57
00:03:00,800 --> 00:03:01,900
I just took over the Group.

58
00:03:02,004 --> 00:03:03,133
My position isn't secure yet.

59
00:03:03,750 --> 00:03:05,000
Some people want me out

60
00:03:05,430 --> 00:03:06,476
and are trying to frame me.

61
00:03:06,960 --> 00:03:07,800
That's normal.

62
00:03:08,493 --> 00:03:10,073
Everything I have comes from the family.

63
00:03:10,630 --> 00:03:11,680
If Luzhou Group falls,

64
00:03:12,750 --> 00:03:13,800
what would I gain?

65
00:03:22,960 --> 00:03:23,800
Tingxiao,

66
00:03:24,430 --> 00:03:25,520
you're my son.

67
00:03:26,360 --> 00:03:28,280
One day, all I have will be yours.

68
00:03:29,120 --> 00:03:30,870
How could I not trust you?

69
00:03:32,430 --> 00:03:34,840
I'm just worried you're too eager

70
00:03:35,800 --> 00:03:36,710
to prove yourself

71
00:03:37,150 --> 00:03:38,310
and might take the wrong path.

72
00:03:40,280 --> 00:03:41,920
Dad, don't worry.

73
00:03:42,840 --> 00:03:44,400
I know what I should do.

74
00:03:46,400 --> 00:03:47,310
Good.

75
00:03:48,800 --> 00:03:49,710
Just remember this:

76
00:03:50,870 --> 00:03:53,240
You should take something I choose

77
00:03:53,590 --> 00:03:54,470
to give you.

78
00:03:55,430 --> 00:03:56,343
You can't take anything

79
00:03:57,030 --> 00:03:58,150
by force.

80
00:03:59,150 --> 00:03:59,990
Understood?

81
00:04:02,120 --> 00:04:02,960
Yes.

82
00:04:04,190 --> 00:04:05,030
Good.

83
00:04:05,360 --> 00:04:06,280
Go handle your work.

84
00:04:07,470 --> 00:04:08,470
I need to get ready too.

85
00:04:09,000 --> 00:04:10,630
I have important people to meet

86
00:04:11,430 --> 00:04:13,080
to settle the mess on Lianxin Island

87
00:04:13,280 --> 00:04:14,560
once and for all.

88
00:04:31,510 --> 00:04:33,070
(I've kept this in for 18 years.)

89
00:04:34,160 --> 00:04:36,430
(I'm not here for your pity.)

90
00:04:42,390 --> 00:04:44,390
Find out how the commercial residence

91
00:04:44,720 --> 00:04:46,430
got construction permits ASAP.

92
00:05:03,750 --> 00:05:05,630
Ms. Lin, as Mr. Lu instructed,

93
00:05:05,830 --> 00:05:07,270
we booked you the best spa suite.

94
00:05:07,360 --> 00:05:08,210
Please go in first.

95
00:05:08,240 --> 00:05:09,160
Mr. Lu will come later.

96
00:05:09,870 --> 00:05:11,400
- Okay, thanks.
- Sure.

97
00:05:14,720 --> 00:05:16,270
(Lu Tingxiao is coming later?)

98
00:05:17,120 --> 00:05:18,630
(Out for thrills in broad daylight.)

99
00:05:18,920 --> 00:05:20,000
(Fate truly favors me.)

100
00:05:21,270 --> 00:05:22,110
(Lin Zhi'er,)

101
00:05:22,600 --> 00:05:23,750
(once this comes out,)

102
00:05:23,950 --> 00:05:25,310
(let's see how you explain it.)

103
00:05:28,510 --> 00:05:29,350
(Tingyu,)

104
00:05:29,600 --> 00:05:31,040
(a friend just saw you)

105
00:05:31,120 --> 00:05:32,160
(and Zhi'er)

106
00:05:32,310 --> 00:05:33,560
(go into a large suite.)

107
00:05:33,986 --> 00:05:35,512
(You two really know how to have fun.)

108
00:05:36,270 --> 00:05:37,270
(Enjoy yourselves.)

109
00:05:42,240 --> 00:05:43,080
Sis,

110
00:05:43,600 --> 00:05:45,870
this place is really nice.

111
00:05:46,950 --> 00:05:47,790
Yeah.

112
00:05:48,600 --> 00:05:49,440
As I told you,

113
00:05:49,480 --> 00:05:51,070
we're fixing those dark circles.

114
00:05:52,560 --> 00:05:53,600
I'll get you a membership.

115
00:05:54,630 --> 00:05:55,720
So generous, Ms. Lin.

116
00:05:56,360 --> 00:05:57,510
You got me spa,

117
00:05:57,680 --> 00:05:58,893
and you'll get me a membership.

118
00:06:00,360 --> 00:06:01,430
Thanks, sis.

119
00:06:02,040 --> 00:06:02,880
It's nothing.

120
00:06:08,310 --> 00:06:09,150
Hello, sir.

121
00:06:10,040 --> 00:06:10,880
Sir.

122
00:06:17,190 --> 00:06:18,830
Sir, this is for female VIPs.

123
00:06:18,870 --> 00:06:19,710
You can't go in.

124
00:06:20,680 --> 00:06:21,520
Women only?

125
00:06:21,680 --> 00:06:22,560
Yes, sir.

126
00:06:29,680 --> 00:06:30,520
Okay.

127
00:06:30,680 --> 00:06:31,640
It's a misunderstanding.

128
00:06:32,270 --> 00:06:33,110
Sorry about this.

129
00:06:42,190 --> 00:06:43,040
I've really lost it.

130
00:06:43,720 --> 00:06:45,310
My wife has suffered enough
as an orphan,

131
00:06:45,750 --> 00:06:47,240
and I thought she'd cheat on me.

132
00:06:48,870 --> 00:06:50,040
I'm really awful.

133
00:07:03,920 --> 00:07:04,760
Move.

134
00:07:26,040 --> 00:07:26,880
What does he want?

135
00:07:29,420 --> 00:07:31,220
(Lu Tingxiao)

136
00:07:36,420 --> 00:07:37,380
(Lu Jianchuan)

137
00:07:39,750 --> 00:07:40,950
Maybe we should head back.

138
00:07:44,240 --> 00:07:45,080
Boss.

139
00:07:45,360 --> 00:07:46,310
I'm on my way.

140
00:07:46,720 --> 00:07:47,630
Almost there.

141
00:07:50,390 --> 00:07:51,360
I'll call Wangzu.

142
00:07:52,120 --> 00:07:53,480
It's too late to stop it now.

143
00:07:59,560 --> 00:08:00,920
Take your people right now

144
00:08:02,270 --> 00:08:03,190
to do something for me.

145
00:08:06,600 --> 00:08:07,440
Yeah.

146
00:08:07,720 --> 00:08:09,270
My skin's all loosened up.

147
00:08:10,310 --> 00:08:11,950
I'm getting an aromatherapy treatment.

148
00:08:12,039 --> 00:08:12,993
Do you want to join me?

149
00:08:13,510 --> 00:08:14,360
I'll pass.

150
00:08:14,870 --> 00:08:16,310
I need to watch my idol's livestream.

151
00:08:16,680 --> 00:08:17,630
I'll watch

152
00:08:17,800 --> 00:08:19,360
while soaking here.

153
00:08:19,680 --> 00:08:20,520
Okay.

154
00:08:20,560 --> 00:08:21,950
If anything comes up, call me.

155
00:08:21,987 --> 00:08:22,986
I'll be right next door.

156
00:08:23,000 --> 00:08:23,840
Okay.

157
00:08:24,560 --> 00:08:25,400
Sis,

158
00:08:26,000 --> 00:08:26,840
what do you think

159
00:08:27,160 --> 00:08:29,070
about me asking Bai to dinner tonight?

160
00:08:30,600 --> 00:08:31,440
Go for it.

161
00:08:31,959 --> 00:08:33,106
I'll wait for your good news.

162
00:08:48,340 --> 00:08:49,020
(Wrong password)

163
00:08:51,220 --> 00:08:54,620
(Unknown caller)

164
00:09:05,020 --> 00:09:08,100
(Loading)

165
00:09:11,260 --> 00:09:15,300
(File transfer)

166
00:09:30,199 --> 00:09:31,265
I'm going to save Wen Yan.

167
00:09:31,600 --> 00:09:32,440
Boss.

168
00:09:32,480 --> 00:09:33,510
AI is everywhere now.

169
00:09:33,723 --> 00:09:34,876
People use it to fake things.

170
00:09:35,150 --> 00:09:36,270
Should we verify it?

171
00:09:39,743 --> 00:09:41,176
(Unknown caller)
This number again.

172
00:09:47,320 --> 00:09:48,160
Hello?

173
00:09:49,080 --> 00:09:49,920
Lu Tingxiao,

174
00:09:50,870 --> 00:09:52,030
look at the photo I sent you.

175
00:09:53,870 --> 00:09:55,136
What are you going to do to her?

176
00:09:56,270 --> 00:09:57,870
She's fine for now.

177
00:09:58,550 --> 00:09:59,390
Don't be nervous.

178
00:10:01,000 --> 00:10:02,670
In a minute, do exactly as I say.

179
00:10:03,200 --> 00:10:05,720
The number you dialed is unavailable.

180
00:10:06,600 --> 00:10:07,440
No answer.

181
00:10:09,870 --> 00:10:11,840
Did Lu Jianchuan tell you to do this?

182
00:10:12,550 --> 00:10:13,390
No questions.

183
00:10:14,000 --> 00:10:14,840
Just do as I say.

184
00:10:17,600 --> 00:10:18,440
What do you want?

185
00:10:18,960 --> 00:10:20,240
My demand is simple.

186
00:10:22,750 --> 00:10:23,910
I want you to stop

187
00:10:24,080 --> 00:10:25,790
everything you're doing,

188
00:10:26,390 --> 00:10:27,600
get out of Luzhou Group,

189
00:10:27,790 --> 00:10:28,670
and go abroad at once.

190
00:10:29,510 --> 00:10:31,080
Don't let me see you again.

191
00:10:32,750 --> 00:10:33,590
Or else,

192
00:10:34,670 --> 00:10:36,910
you'll never see the woman
you love again.

193
00:10:42,080 --> 00:10:43,013
Don't do anything rash.

194
00:10:43,910 --> 00:10:45,360
I want to hear her voice now.

195
00:10:58,320 --> 00:10:59,160
Talk.

196
00:11:01,870 --> 00:11:02,750
Talk to him.

197
00:11:04,750 --> 00:11:06,030
Talk to him!

198
00:11:09,910 --> 00:11:11,360
Talk!

199
00:11:14,400 --> 00:11:15,130
(Bai,)

200
00:11:15,141 --> 00:11:16,779
(Wen Yan and I are
at the spa treatment.)

201
00:11:16,790 --> 00:11:18,480
(Shall we have dinner after this?)

202
00:11:18,780 --> 00:11:21,700
(Qing)

203
00:11:24,020 --> 00:11:25,860
(Unknown caller)

204
00:11:31,870 --> 00:11:32,710
Bai.

205
00:11:32,840 --> 00:11:33,680
Qing,

206
00:11:33,960 --> 00:11:35,200
are you with Wen Yan right now?

207
00:11:35,510 --> 00:11:36,450
I can't reach her phone.

208
00:11:37,440 --> 00:11:38,280
Wen Yan?

209
00:11:38,870 --> 00:11:40,270
She's next door doing therapy.

210
00:11:40,630 --> 00:11:41,490
It'll take a while.

211
00:11:41,510 --> 00:11:42,720
I guess she fell asleep.

212
00:11:42,960 --> 00:11:44,550
Go check if she's safe, now.

213
00:11:45,480 --> 00:11:46,870
Now? Why?

214
00:11:47,030 --> 00:11:48,270
No time to explain. Go, now.

215
00:11:48,840 --> 00:11:49,680
Okay, okay.

216
00:12:05,750 --> 00:12:07,120
She's right in front of me.

217
00:12:07,200 --> 00:12:08,040
She's perfectly safe.

218
00:12:09,080 --> 00:12:09,920
Okay.

219
00:12:12,120 --> 00:12:12,960
It's fake.

220
00:12:17,270 --> 00:12:18,390
Tell him to come save you.

221
00:12:18,720 --> 00:12:19,750
Have him come save you!

222
00:12:21,440 --> 00:12:23,390
Say something!

223
00:12:25,910 --> 00:12:27,600
Enough. Drop the act.

224
00:12:31,480 --> 00:12:33,200
With photos and voice clips,

225
00:12:34,270 --> 00:12:35,870
you came prepared.

226
00:12:38,840 --> 00:12:40,030
What was it you said just now?

227
00:12:40,790 --> 00:12:42,390
That I should leave Luzhou Group?

228
00:12:43,630 --> 00:12:44,470
That's right.

229
00:12:46,720 --> 00:12:48,240
Let me make this clear:

230
00:12:49,000 --> 00:12:50,000
Not a chance.

231
00:13:06,680 --> 00:13:08,130
♪This door♪

232
00:13:08,530 --> 00:13:13,280
♪Lets in the sky outside♪

233
00:13:13,760 --> 00:13:17,320
♪With a voice even lighter♪

234
00:13:17,320 --> 00:13:20,130
♪Than how you just greeted me♪

235
00:13:20,580 --> 00:13:21,950
♪I know now♪

236
00:13:22,280 --> 00:13:27,160
♪What the chill in my body means♪

237
00:13:27,510 --> 00:13:30,380
♪The moment salt hits the wound♪

238
00:13:30,580 --> 00:13:34,000
♪My heart still beats so naively♪

239
00:13:34,170 --> 00:13:37,160
♪To complete♪

240
00:13:37,620 --> 00:13:41,370
♪A joy that needs no brave pretense♪

241
00:13:41,510 --> 00:13:44,010
♪How cruel sincerity can be♪

242
00:13:44,150 --> 00:13:47,700
♪Like a door with no key♪

243
00:13:48,010 --> 00:13:50,330
♪Maybe you just passed by♪

244
00:13:50,330 --> 00:13:53,910
♪The tears in my eyes♪

245
00:13:54,620 --> 00:13:57,170
♪You looked like you had nothing to say♪

246
00:13:57,170 --> 00:13:58,910
♪Then got so good at being cold♪

247
00:13:58,910 --> 00:14:01,750
♪That's why a smile feels so precious♪

248
00:14:01,960 --> 00:14:04,050
♪Maybe you just passed by♪

249
00:14:04,200 --> 00:14:08,530
♪The tears burned into my heart♪

250
00:14:08,910 --> 00:14:11,200
♪Let's say silence was just for show♪

251
00:14:11,200 --> 00:14:15,870
♪Even if I've grown another year♪
